---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="[C3_NAME] is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit that builds free, open-source apps for families."
>

<section class="hero" style="padding:4rem 1.5rem;">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label" style="color:#c8a060;">About Us</p>
    <h1>Strengthening families through free, open tools.</h1>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="content">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      [C3_NAME] is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization dedicated to supporting
      families through research, education, and the development of free public
      tools.
    </p>
    <p>
      We believe that the digital tools families use every day should work
      <em>for</em> them — not harvest their data, not demand subscriptions,
      and not require surrendering privacy for basic functionality. We build
      apps that reflect those values, and we give them away for free.
    </p>

    <h2>What We Build</h2>
    <p>
      Our apps are practical tools for everyday family life: video journals,
      daily capture, family records, and more. Every app is:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Free to download and use</strong> — no fees, no freemium tiers</li>
      <li><strong>Open source</strong> — code is publicly auditable on GitHub</li>
      <li><strong>Local-first</strong> — your data stays on your device</li>
      <li><strong>No-account</strong> — no sign-up, no email, no profile</li>
      <li><strong>No tracking</strong> — no analytics, no telemetry, no advertising</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>
      [C3_NAME] is a young organization. We are a small team that believes
      families deserve better software than the ad-supported, data-harvesting
      mainstream alternatives.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you share that conviction and want to help — through volunteering,
      development contributions, or financial support — we would love to hear
      from you.
    </p>

    <h2>Nonprofit Status</h2>
    <p>
      [C3_NAME] is organized as a 501(c)(3) tax-exempt nonprofit under the
      Internal Revenue Code. Contributions are tax-deductible to the extent
      permitted by law.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our apps are the organization's primary programmatic activity and
      represent our commitment to public benefit. They are not products of a
      commercial venture.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about our organization, partnership inquiries, or grant
      opportunities: <a href="/contact">contact us here</a> or email
      <a href="mailto:hello@[C3_DOMAIN].org">hello@[C3_DOMAIN].org</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
